Sum of Even Numbers till N
Send Feedback
Given a number N, print sum of all even numbers from 1 to N.
Input Format :
Integer N
Output Format :
Required Sum 
Sample Input 1 :
 6
Sample Output 1 :
12

#include <iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){
    int sum=0,n=0,x=0;
    cin >> n;
    while (x<=n)
        {
        sum=sum + x;
        x+=2;
        }
    cout << sum;
}
